headline: 1 Industrials Stock to Target This Week and 2 We Question
summary: Even if they go mostly unnoticed, industrial businesses are the backbone of our country. Their momentum is also rising as lower interest rates have incentivized higher capital spending. As a result, the industry has posted a 7.5% gain over the past six months, beating the S&P 500 by 2.1 percentage points.
